NAME = misc-powersave-cpu-scaling
PATCH = misc/${NAME}.patch
TITLE = Powersave CPU Scaling
DESCRIPTION = This patch enables CPU scaling by enabling the ondemand governor. It sets the max CPU speed to 600Mhz and min to 250MHz. If you want to change this, edit /etc/event.d/powersave-cpu-scaling. Make sure you reboot after applying this patch for it to take effect. WARNING: Do not apply the SmartReflex patch if you use this patch. It will cause your webOS device to crash.
